    android.arch.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.DialogInterface.OnCancelListener, android.content.DialogInterface.OnDismissListener, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class ConfirmDialog
extends android.support.v4.app.DialogFragment
    A dialog fragment that will will work with an activity, user must bundle in the dialog title, message, and cancel/confirm button text. This implements an interface that is called within the activity to see if the user confirmed/cancelled the dialog interaction
